    <abstract>
      <t>PCE is used to distribute a binding SID with a list of SIDs to a node. This document describes extensions to PCEP for distributing the binding SID with the list of SIDs and an identifier of the node. When detecting the failure of the node, an neighbor of the node protects the binding SID of the failed node.</t>
